    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >某天早晨，杰克被从平凡的生活中撕裂出来，困在了一个奇异的世界里。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他唯一的武器是一根旧的弹簧跳杆，凭借它，他开始了对神秘维度未知高度的攀登。在这个重力异常、地面不稳定的领域里，杰克唯一的目标就是不断向上攀爬。但没有人知道顶端等待着的是什么——是出口，还是更大的谜团？他唯一能确定的是，只有爬到终点，他才能找到答案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/212b605e50b3d0ad52f45381a047d917.poster.avif?t=1762956583\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/212b605e50b3d0ad52f45381a047d917.webm?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/212b605e50b3d0ad52f45381a047d917.mp4?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个失误就能让你前功尽弃！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在杰克的世界里，没有第二次机会。没有存档按钮或检查点，一次小小的失误就能让你重回起点。这种无情的挑战会将你的耐心推向极限，真正考验你重整旗鼓的能力——字面意义上地“反弹”回来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/fdbb2307e746b6f8c9d0827b3056a6ac.poster.avif?t=1762956583\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/fdbb2307e746b6f8c9d0827b3056a6ac.webm?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/fdbb2307e746b6f8c9d0827b3056a6ac.mp4?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战胜不可预知的挑战！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杰克周围的世界不仅仅是一个背景，它充满了各种元素，这些元素既能帮助你前进，也可能阻碍你的进展。从意外的助力提升到让你偏离路线的陷阱，你需要快速的反应和敏锐的头脑才能顺利通过。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/5c287acf3594d06f5dc6cc82cb94dc2c.poster.avif?t=1762956583\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/5c287acf3594d06f5dc6cc82cb94dc2c.webm?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/5c287acf3594d06f5dc6cc82cb94dc2c.mp4?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >笑、哭、怒——然后再来一次！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杰克的旅程不仅仅是攀爬，更是关于你在过程中经历的情感。游戏的难度曲线是刻意设计得如此惩罚性，每一次辛苦获得的胜利都会带来真正的成就感——当然，也伴随着无尽的挫折感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/f99e8c955716408eb18ddf2d0865694b.poster.avif?t=1762956583\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/f99e8c955716408eb18ddf2d0865694b.webm?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/f99e8c955716408eb18ddf2d0865694b.mp4?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有存档——每次失误都会让你回到起点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内置速通计时器和高度追踪器，适合竞技玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >助力和障碍并存，使每次攀登都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个超现实、违背重力的世界，充满不可预知的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富有挑战性的难度曲线，将考验你的毅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
